Study periods

Distribution of event time by variant types. Severe cases are red, cases with markers are green. Will add another plot using calendar date when that info is added to the mapped data

We chose 100/101 days post D57 to break the follow-up period into two because all Delta cases and all severe happened after that.

min(subset(dat_mapped,EventIndPrimaryType_short=="Del",EventTimePrimaryD57),na.rm=T)
## [1] 120

Missingness and imputation

Correlation is high between bAb markers, but moderate between the two nAb markers.

dat=subset(dat_mapped, EarlyinfectionD57==0 & Perprotocol==1 & Bserostatus==0 & Trt==1)
dat=dat[,"Day57"%.%assays]
names(dat)=sub("Day57","",names(dat))
mypairs(dat)

A closer look at the correlation between ancestral ID50 and Delta ID50

corplot(Day57pseudoneutid50_D614G~Day57pseudoneutid50_Delta, dat_mapped, asp=1)

bAb markers are all-or-none. For nAb, we will require Delta nAb to be present. For the 9 ptids without ancestral nAb but with Delta nAb, we will impute the ancestral nAb. There are a lot more ptids with just ancestral nAb but we wont use them in the correlates study to allow comparison between Delta and ancestral nAb.

dat=subset(dat_mapped, EarlyinfectionD57==0 & Perprotocol==1 & Bserostatus==0 & Trt==1)
for (i in 1:length(assays)) {
  dat[['tmp'%.%i]]=ifelse(is.na(dat[['Day57'%.%assays[i]]]), 0, 1)
}
dat$tmp=with(dat,paste0(tmp1,tmp2,tmp3,tmp4,tmp5,tmp6,tmp7,tmp8,tmp9,tmp10))
print(table(dat$tmp, dat$DeltaEventIndD57_7to303))
##             
##                  0     1
##   0000000000 15522   253
##   0011111111     8     4
##   0111111111     9     5
##   1000000000   521     5
##   1011111111    22     7
##   1100000000    23     3
##   1111111111   135    45

We will only impute ancestral nAb using Delta nAb. We will have two sets of weights, one for bAb and one for nAb.

dat=subset(dat_mapped)
dat$tmp1 = !is.na(dat$Day57pseudoneutid50_Delta)
dat$tmp2 = !is.na(dat$Day57bindSpike_Alpha)
dat$tmp=with(dat,paste0(as.integer(tmp1),as.integer(tmp2)))
print(table(dat$tmp, dat$DeltaEventIndD57_7to303))

##          0     1
##   00 24038   281

##   11   144    51
